OL,3,CThree men jailed after farming #2.3m
OL,4,Cof cannabis
OL,6,FThree men have been jailed after
OL,7,Ffarming #2.3m of cannabis in a
OL,8,FScottish Borders town.
OL,10,FLoarent Balla, 21, Joanis Melcani, 27,
OL,11,FBesim Veliya, 63, and Seheptim Halil,
OL,12,F36, all appeared on drug supply
OL,13,Fcharges at Selkirk Sheriff Court on 6
OL,14,FJanuary 2025.
OL,16,FPolice Scotland found nearly 3,000
OL,17,Fcannabis plants during a raid of two
OL,18,Fbuildings - known locally as the
OL,19,Fformer Woolworths and Ladbrokes shops
OL,20,F- on Channel Street, the town centre
OL,21,Fof Galashiels, on 26 March 2024.
