OL,3,CThree men jailed after farming #2.3m
OL,4,Cof cannabis
OL,6,FSheriff Peter Patterson sentenced
OL,7,FBesim Veliya to 21 months in prison,
OL,8,FJoanis Melcani to two years, and
OL,9,FLoarent Balla to 18 months. All of the
OL,10,Fjail time has been backdated to their
OL,11,Farrest in March 2024.
OL,13,FThe sentencing of Shepetim Halil was
OL,14,Fdeferred until the end of January
OL,15,Fafter he refused to cooperate with the
OL,16,Finterpreter.
OL,18,FA fifth man, Petrit Musta, 48, was
OL,19,Fsentenced to 28 months in prison for
OL,20,Fsimilar drug charges in December 2024.
